  "reference_number": "RUS2057",
  "remarks": "\nNOVIKOMBANK is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the following ground: NOVIKOMBANK is involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia through carrying on business in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, namely the Russian financial services sector.\n",
